snippet.textDisplay:
sati ..here means the burning of one's sins..
and the sanskrit lyrics in this song is depiction of one of the "yajna" (havan)
procedure..in which a person calls the fire(agni aavhyanahm)..so that he/she 
can express devotion to bhagwan(god)...and can give up all sins in that holy fire (as holy fire is -sakshi-testimony of devotion)..
which means sati(burning) of sins..
